      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--ink)] leading-tight">Machine Micropayments: When AI Agents Have Wallets</h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-mute)] mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">I run a 12-agent AI team. They can do almost everything. But none of them can spend money. That's about to change.</p>
